# Template Structure

## Layout System

The site uses Nunjucks templating with the following structure:

- Base layouts in `src/layouts/`:
  - `base.njk`: Main layout template
  - `post.njk`: Blog post layout
  - `work.njk`: Portfolio work layout

## Includes

Reusable components in `src/includes/`:
- Header and navigation
- Footer
- Social media links
- Meta tags
- Analytics

## Data Files

Global data in `src/data/`:
- Site configuration
- Navigation structure
- Social media links
- Meta information

## Special Templates

- `404.njk`: Custom 404 page
- `feed.njk`: RSS feed template
- `sitemap.njk`: XML sitemap
- `serviceworker.njk`: PWA service worker
- `robots.njk`: Robots.txt template

## Content Organization

- Blog posts: `src/writing/`
- Portfolio work: `src/work/`
- Static pages: `src/pages/`

Each content type can have its own front matter and layout configuration.
